title: Queen_the film_made_in_heaven
description:
DVD Release Date: 24 Mar 2003
 Run Time: 55 minutes
 Audio: Dolby Didgital


Video Description
Featuring the following films:

I was born to Love You "I was born to Love You" - director Richard = Heslop
Evolution "Heaven for Everyone" - director Simon Pummell
Heart-Ache "Too Much Love will Kill You" - director Simon Pummell
O "My Life has been Saved" - director Nichola Bruce
You Don't Fool Me "You Don't Fool Me" - director Mark Szaszy
Outside-In "A Winter's Tale" - directore Chris Rodley
Return Trip "Let Me Live" - director Bernard Rudden
Mother Love "Mother Love" - director Jim Gillespie


Synopsis
Original video footage commissioned by Queen and co-produced by the British Film Institute. Nine short films accompany tracks from Queen's uplifting final album, MADE IN HEAVEN, completed shortly after the passing of Freddie Mercury. Originally screened at the 1996 Cannes Film Festival.
